Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，还叫你来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会，没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在开始忙起来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说必须跟你谈谈\n我们的事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指秘银的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，是你跟我之间的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:01:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听者(Whispered)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你应该也已经发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是其中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#20 Venom之火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听者(Whispered)被称为\n 黑科技的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只要条件齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能提供远超越现代的\n科学理论与技术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你至今发挥过两次那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次是在兴凯自治区的山里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次是与贝希摩斯战斗时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论哪次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都知道了\n自己绝不可能知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过第二次算是我帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要，我有事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时发生了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时产生了“共鸣”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共鸣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听者(Whispered)可以在精神深处\n共同分享彼此的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我与你彼此强烈的\n感觉到需要对方时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会产生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常危险的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽可能的避免\n倾听者(Whispered)的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真有那么方便的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的事物\n通常都具有两面刃的特性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听者(Whispered)的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即所谓的思想共享
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是指对话或通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是彼此融合一体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,譬如像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法将茶跟牛奶分开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走错一步的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会连自己是谁都无法分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…似懂非懂的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我尽是在做抽象的比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是其实我也不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以会对你说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为无论\n倾听者(Whispered)的力量是好是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有人想要得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫九龙的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，他们想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道我也是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也会连我一起抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此不论多卑鄙的事情\n他们大概都会去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你并不是孤立无援的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们秘银
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会让你落入敌人手里的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以宗介才会跟着我是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那么会惹麻烦的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是连听都没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上虽然说着“我要保护你”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却只会轰轰烈烈的自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那简直跟战队卡通的小喽啰\n没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看了也不会腻\n这倒是不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我可没有举白旗投降喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常在基地里\n我也常跟他见面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人一起溜出基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无人的沙滩上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙…沙滩上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这个人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就扯平了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不是说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟那家伙不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前已经跟大家说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美军的设施被武装集团占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点是昂柳共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝利达欧岛的生物武器拆解基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里保存了数百吨的神经瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当事的武装集团扬言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不接受要求的话\n就要散布储藏室的瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要的任务是制压敌方AS\n与确保人质安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及阻止重要设施遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方战力目前有九架AS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与自走战车Triple A五辆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为这架AS\n是苏联的新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是Savage(野蛮人)的后继机种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,针对这架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已知可以用\n一般的机体与战术来对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架最需注意的敌方AS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架机体搭载了某种特殊机械
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的攻击手段完全无效
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果遇上这架AS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量避免直接交战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说，就是快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们逃跑？太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不如一开始\n就不要攻击还比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的“逃跑”并不是建议或请求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违反的人我会予以严惩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是如果你们还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于称呼方便\n我们叫这架AS为“Venom(猛毒)”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与Venom(猛毒)交战\n并破坏它的这项任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交由相良士官执行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭遇Venom(猛毒)时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人会后退援护你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以联合攻击跟肉搏战缠住他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让他有休息的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来一定会有胜利的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被打败了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战就告失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方大概就会一个不剩的\n成为Venom(猛毒)的饵食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是少校也真残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道上次阿富汗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还对他说那种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说印度洋部队那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全把宗介当成杀人凶手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过除了他以外\n其他人都进坟墓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这么想也是无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也是一副\n自己也死掉就好了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴虽然没说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，你是因为担心我而来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要露出那种表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会回到你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然要不要到驾驶舱内…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是上次的任务遇上点小问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下就要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，打扰到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在深度80，速度3海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EMFC没问题\n(electromagnetic field cancel，电磁流体控制器)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潮流向南东2海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海上吹着微风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AS用气密室，ALL GREEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一到第六号的气密室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一号到第六号的气密室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的任务从水中出动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六架AS共分成三组
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分别为突击班\n狙击班、炸弹处理班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突击班是马卡兰与相良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狙击班是威巴与关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹处理班是毛跟达尼刚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过路线点后\n各自前往指定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AS用舱门全部开启
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AS用舱门全部开启
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被打败了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战就告失败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方大概就会一个不剩的\n成为Venom(猛毒)的饵食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？毛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是给自己压力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个频道其他人听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那没关系，我….
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只小要\n你连我们都想一起保护吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你的好意\n不过不需要你的操心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是克鲁兹、马卡兰\n或是其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概也都会这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是，我会记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是听话的好孩子，没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛1号呼叫全员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已通过路线点3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照预定，现在开始分成三组
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛2号，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛6号，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛7号，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛10号，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛12号，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有这么凑巧的地下隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连圣诞老人都会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的\n竟然在海底玩土拨鼠游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要出这种任务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要发牢骚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只有我们办得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就算设施的炸弹爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,损伤也不会有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许住这里的穷人会翘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达尼刚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啦，不要当真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这不是作战时应讲的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不谨慎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦，不要太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好完成任务的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望最好是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐他们能顺利完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们失败的话\n我们也只能开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我在毒气里面干架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薪水我还嫌少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘银的装备跟薪水\n虽然都不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过做法太拖拖拉拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要你保护人质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就是叫你注意生物武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是普通的突击队\n待遇是不会这么好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R，把马力等级调成MIL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,gpl MIL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输出功率上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛2号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功拆除引爆装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在将前往地面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛6号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以出动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛10号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,80，90，100
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛1号呼叫全员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩猎解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由M9的ADM收到\n交战开始的讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请升起所有ECS柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MBT正常开启\n(main balast tank，主压舱)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛10号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有看得到的对空炮\n都加以破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛6号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我这里看得到的目标都解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多送点敌人过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛12号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已镇压及确保宿舍B安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人质平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛2号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已镇压及确保宿舍A安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现23名人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛7号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击毁四架敌方AS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛1号呼叫全员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没遇到Venom(猛毒)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没反应，没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没反…不，有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在开什么玩笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？野牛2号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘银的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想念你们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘了在沙漠的那笔帐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派对开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛1号呼叫野牛6号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有办法狙击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个位置无法取得射击路线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛10号，飞弹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用完了，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛7号，前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人后退，进行援护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7号，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是之前说的魔术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要靠近那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛2号呼叫全员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要瞄准机体\n试着瞄准武器看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准格林机关炮的弹匣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
