Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是轻微损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛7号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作变单调了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达尼刚，退下
