Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛被打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点送她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么刚才不能用？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我，R
