Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Venom(猛毒)引到岛的东侧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到刚才那栋大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什么？
