Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立场跟上次完全颠倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任你宰割吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九龙，你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不开枪吗？
